# Doodlash Canvas & Realtime

- Sync **stroke vectors** only — never send raw `ImageData`.
- Flood-fill runs on the **drawer client**; broadcast result via `canvas_fill` (special fill stroke).
- **Undo:** Drawer keeps last 20 strokes locally; on undo emit `canvas_undo` with full `strokes[]`; server replaces `room.strokes` and broadcasts.
- **Clear:** `canvas_clear` clears server `room.strokes` for the turn.
- Client countdown is visual only; reconcile with `timer_sync` every 5s.
- Drawer cannot submit guesses; chat input disabled while drawing.
- Guesses must match the **full** answer string (case-insensitive, trimmed) per SDD §6.8.
